Such part or parts of the area herein reserved as socialized housing and declared open for disposition which are being used or earmarked for quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 27th day of Jan, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

( Sgd .) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: ( Sgd .) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

